  24 Apr 2002; Thilo Bangert <bangert@gentoo.org> files/consolelog.sh :
  initial release

  24 Apr 2002; Thilo Bangert <bangert@gentoo.org> matalog-0.6-r9.ebuild :  
  added consolelog.sh - script to be able to log to a console - from LFS
  
